Cell["\<\
In the earlier version of Q3, a Fermion should be given at least one Flavor \
index. Otherwise, its Vacuum was regarded as Void. In more recent versions, \
this is not true any longer.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->1123164233,ExpressionUUID->"503dfc13-80fe-4b5b-a464-1abc2c311b6f"],

